### Tokenization Engine

#### [NEW] [tokenizer.js](file:///d:/Averon/tokenizer.js)

Takes AI analysis results and creates tokens.

**Logic:**
```
Input:  Asset value = ₹50,000 | Raise amount = ₹5,000 | Risk score = 25%
Output: 10 tokens × 500 Averon Coin each

Factors:
- Lower risk → fewer, higher-value tokens (more investor-friendly)
- Higher risk → more, smaller tokens (spreads risk)
- Min token price: 10 AC | Max token price: 5000 AC
- Min tokens: 2 | Max tokens: 1000
```

