### Capital Raising & Payout System

#### [NEW] [capital.js](file:///d:/Averon/capital.js)

Handles the flow when an asset is fully funded.

**When all tokens are sold:**
1. Asset status → `funded`
2. Total Averon Coins collected → converted to INR at current rate
3. Asset owner receives payout (recorded, actual transfer via Razorpay if configured)
4. Averon Coin price increases (+2-5% per funded asset, scaled by raise amount)
5. All token holders now own fractional rights to the asset
6. Blockchain: FUND_COMPLETE transaction recorded

