### P2P Coin Trading

#### [NEW] [marketplace.js](file:///d:/Averon/marketplace.js)

Simple order-book-style peer-to-peer trading.

**How it works:**
- Sellers place sell orders: "I want to sell X Averon Coins at ₹Y each"
- Buyers place buy orders: "I want to buy X Averon Coins at ₹Y each"
- When a buy order matches a sell order → trade executes automatically
- Trade creates TRANSFER transactions on the blockchain
- Order book visible to all users

**API:**
- `POST /api/market/sell` — place a sell order
- `POST /api/market/buy` — place a buy order
- `GET /api/market/orderbook` — view current orders
- `GET /api/market/trades` — recent trades
- `DELETE /api/market/order/:id` — cancel an order

